It would be exceedingly rare for either of

00:17:45.194 --> 00:17:49.135
them to be covenants since covenant has

00:17:49.195 --> 00:17:51.896
included no one up to the previous

00:17:51.936 --> 00:17:54.297
twenty-four years and now is one in a

00:17:54.336 --> 00:17:54.717
million.

00:17:55.436 --> 00:17:58.397
No, they're not.

00:17:58.438 --> 00:18:00.417
Two people acting badly.

00:18:01.478 --> 00:18:03.318
That child has every reason to live.

00:18:03.338 --> 00:18:04.419
It's the child's fault.

00:18:06.288 --> 00:18:08.689
but this was no ordinary man.

00:18:10.049 --> 00:18:13.031
This is the chosen one.

00:18:13.071 --> 00:18:14.853
This is the son of God.

00:18:16.433 --> 00:18:18.355
This is the Messiah and the returning

00:18:18.414 --> 00:18:19.115
king.

00:18:20.476 --> 00:18:22.897
And for him, under those circumstances,

00:18:24.117 --> 00:18:25.098
it was not appropriate.

00:18:30.321 --> 00:18:33.124
And so if Dowd didn't receive the message

00:18:33.223 --> 00:18:35.164
loud and clear, well,

00:18:37.272 --> 00:18:42.755
we wouldn't be here.

00:18:42.796 --> 00:18:48.518
God was uncompromising in this regard.

00:18:48.538 --> 00:18:54.161
The king's introduction is sufficient to

00:18:54.381 --> 00:18:59.522
tell us everything we need to know about

00:18:59.583 --> 00:19:00.644
what follows.

00:19:01.644 --> 00:19:03.704
This was what he wrote

00:19:05.426 --> 00:19:10.810
Immediately after, God dressed him down.

00:19:10.830 --> 00:19:11.711
He was angry.

00:19:12.912 --> 00:19:13.752
He was depressed.

00:19:14.534 --> 00:19:16.335
He was likely intoxicated,

00:19:16.875 --> 00:19:18.596
drinking way too much wine.

00:19:19.676 --> 00:19:21.598
He was thinking with the wrong head,

00:19:21.659 --> 00:19:23.660
as they say.

00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:24.780
He was out of his mind.

00:19:25.661 --> 00:19:27.182
What I'm going to share with you now

00:19:28.663 --> 00:19:32.145
is easily the most despicable song ever

00:19:32.405 --> 00:19:33.346
written by someone.

00:19:35.127 --> 00:19:36.229
who is familiar with Yahowah.

00:19:38.050 --> 00:19:39.751
It will be hard to present this to

00:19:39.791 --> 00:19:39.912
you.

00:19:40.873 --> 00:19:43.675
And you're going to notice in this

00:19:43.715 --> 00:19:48.259
throughout, I'm copying an attitude.

00:19:48.539 --> 00:19:49.500
I am relentless.

00:19:50.521 --> 00:19:52.623
I will say every step of the way,

00:19:53.763 --> 00:19:55.806
what's wrong is wrong.

00:19:56.366 --> 00:20:00.410
I'm not going to take Dowd's side.

00:20:00.430 --> 00:20:01.711
Yahowah doesn't.

00:20:01.832 --> 00:20:02.152
I won't.

00:20:03.823 --> 00:20:05.763
Now, that said,

00:20:08.385 --> 00:20:09.666
my wife and I do intervene.

00:20:10.287 --> 00:20:12.167
This is one of the most important

00:20:12.208 --> 00:20:13.970
interventions of all of human history.

00:20:14.009 --> 00:20:16.330
I'm going to share the details of that

00:20:16.391 --> 00:20:18.412
with you as we move through this process.

00:20:19.173 --> 00:20:22.335
And it is an extraordinary finding in how

00:20:22.375 --> 00:20:23.276
all of that occurs.

00:20:24.576 --> 00:20:25.356
But at this moment,

00:20:25.636 --> 00:20:26.897
we had not yet done so.

00:20:26.958 --> 00:20:28.638
And we probably would not do so for

00:20:28.679 --> 00:20:29.859
the next decade.

00:20:31.126 --> 00:20:33.907
I think of the fourteen years between this

00:20:33.988 --> 00:20:38.931
event and the end of Dowd's first of

00:20:38.971 --> 00:20:39.790
three lives.

00:20:41.112 --> 00:20:42.612
He just wallowed in misery.

00:20:42.652 --> 00:20:44.173
It was one mistake after another.

00:20:45.913 --> 00:20:47.294
I think it was during the last four

00:20:47.334 --> 00:20:51.115
years of this existence and then first

00:20:51.155 --> 00:20:55.518
four years of Solomon's reign when Solomon

00:20:55.557 --> 00:20:56.218
took the throne.

00:20:56.317 --> 00:20:57.499
He was only twelve years old.

00:20:58.939 --> 00:20:59.960
He needed some parenting.

00:21:02.882 --> 00:21:07.605
So this is before our intervention.

00:21:07.726 --> 00:21:08.346
It begins.

00:21:09.627 --> 00:21:14.411
To the Natsach, the enduring director,

00:21:15.352 --> 00:21:16.712
the eternal conductor,

00:21:18.173 --> 00:21:21.057
for the continuously supervised.

00:21:22.557 --> 00:21:23.878
It's a Mizmowr, a song.

00:21:25.220 --> 00:21:27.261
A psalm of Down.

00:21:28.663 --> 00:21:30.304
When Nathan, giving,

00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:35.753
The Naby prophet came to him regarding the

00:21:35.794 --> 00:21:40.517
relationship upon him pursuing after

00:21:41.116 --> 00:21:43.979
Bathsheba, promised daughter.

