Pretty clear when this one was first

00:21:50.663 --> 00:21:50.942
uttered.

00:21:53.176 --> 00:21:55.698
So looking at this with older and wiser

00:21:55.958 --> 00:21:56.318
eyes,

00:21:56.378 --> 00:21:58.298
there is another pertinent way to

00:21:58.378 --> 00:22:01.760
interpret the otherwise common la Natsach,

00:22:02.060 --> 00:22:03.902
enduring director, introduction.

