01:09:26.154 --> 01:09:28.176
They're beside me, all around me,

01:09:28.756 --> 01:09:32.157
closely corresponding to me because they

01:09:32.216 --> 01:09:36.939
continually proclaim what I have become.

01:09:39.038 --> 01:09:41.239
They remain in plain sight right in front

01:09:41.279 --> 01:09:41.500
of me.

01:09:42.225 --> 01:09:44.826
ahead of me and trailing me and clearly

01:09:44.886 --> 01:09:47.726
and constantly announcing and expounding

01:09:47.766 --> 01:09:54.229
upon who I have presently become.

01:09:54.270 --> 01:09:54.489
Ms.

01:09:54.529 --> 01:09:55.229
Moore, Psalm.

01:09:56.291 --> 01:09:57.211
Fifty-one, three.

01:10:02.873 --> 01:10:06.194
