Now,

01:10:45.472 --> 01:10:47.913
I would be remiss if I didn't reveal

01:10:47.953 --> 01:10:51.715
that Tamyd continually, persistently,

01:10:51.854 --> 01:10:57.016
perpetually is just one letter away from

01:10:57.176 --> 01:10:57.637
