01:11:14.118 --> 01:11:19.400
the YM suffix on tamym makes tam a

01:11:19.461 --> 01:11:20.542
plural adjective,

01:11:21.221 --> 01:11:25.144
and tamyd continuing to be persistent,

01:11:25.225 --> 01:11:26.465
and tamym,

01:11:27.405 --> 01:11:29.907
the word errantly rendered perfect,

01:11:30.747 --> 01:11:33.689
share the same actionable root, tamam.

01:11:35.706 --> 01:11:40.109
And therein is one of life's great

01:11:40.689 --> 01:11:41.310
lessons.

01:11:43.810 --> 01:11:48.274
Yahowah is not seeking perfection as it

01:11:48.293 --> 01:11:51.577
would serve no purpose and it would be

01:11:51.636 --> 01:11:54.779
tragically counterproductive.

01:11:56.079 --> 01:11:56.840
If we were perfect,

01:11:58.140 --> 01:11:59.301
there would be nothing to learn

01:12:00.154 --> 01:12:01.135
no way to grow,

01:12:01.914 --> 01:12:03.676
no opportunity for improvement,

01:12:04.195 --> 01:12:07.658
no capacity for us to be unique or

01:12:07.757 --> 01:12:10.079
interesting.

01:12:10.119 --> 01:12:13.601
God wasn't expecting or even desirous of

01:12:13.742 --> 01:12:17.003
