01:12:43.395 --> 01:12:43.994
the job.

01:12:45.095 --> 01:12:47.497
Life is a test,

01:12:48.377 --> 01:12:50.677
and the passing grade is demonstrating

01:12:50.978 --> 01:12:53.259
that we're eager to be perceptive,

01:12:53.679 --> 01:12:57.161
reflective, responsive, and reliable.

01:12:58.993 --> 01:13:00.734
Listen, learn, engage,

01:13:01.293 --> 01:13:10.797
and then continue until the job is done.

01:13:10.858 --> 01:13:14.420
This is what the religious miss when they

01:13:14.460 --> 01:13:17.201
