01:13:25.082 --> 01:13:27.463
Dowd fulfilled his mission.

01:13:28.024 --> 01:13:30.345
He completed the most difficult and

01:13:30.405 --> 01:13:33.567
demanding challenge that any man has ever

01:13:33.606 --> 01:13:34.027
faced.

01:13:35.207 --> 01:13:38.269
He endured crucifixion to open the door to

01:13:38.408 --> 01:13:40.130
life on Pesach,

01:13:40.550 --> 01:13:43.492
and he went into hell on Matsah to

01:13:43.532 --> 01:13:47.734
remove his guilt and ours.

01:13:47.833 --> 01:13:48.234
Therefore,

01:13:48.293 --> 01:13:51.636
my critique of him is because I, too,

01:13:53.645 --> 01:13:54.726
have a job to complete.

01:13:55.367 --> 01:13:58.029
And it includes reestablishing Dowd's

01:13:58.088 --> 01:14:00.371
relationship with the Yahowah and then

01:14:00.451 --> 01:14:03.712
restoring his reputation with his people

01:14:03.912 --> 01:14:09.077
because only then is the job complete.

01:14:09.636 --> 01:14:10.677
And in the present moment,

01:14:11.738 --> 01:14:13.439
prior to our intervention,

01:14:14.761 --> 01:14:17.122
the king simply doubled down on Chata.

01:14:18.430 --> 01:14:21.230
going away and becoming misleading by

01:14:21.390 --> 01:14:22.831
using the verbal route.

01:14:23.110 --> 01:14:24.912
And then Dowd would add a dose of

01:14:24.992 --> 01:14:29.512
raw evil ineptitude into the mix.

01:14:29.533 --> 01:14:35.493
But I think I've said enough for today.

01:14:37.354 --> 01:14:39.114
I'm going to conclude this program at this

01:14:39.175 --> 01:14:40.655
point.

01:14:40.815 --> 01:14:42.336
And we're going to pick this back up

01:14:42.416 --> 01:14:45.896
after an hour and fifteen minutes

01:14:45.917 --> 01:14:46.277
tomorrow.

01:14:50.752 --> 01:14:56.494
I am in one breath sad that I

01:14:56.555 --> 01:15:01.578
have to expose my beloved son and our

01:15:01.618 --> 01:15:05.980
King in this way.

01:15:06.100 --> 01:15:11.064
And I am in the next honored to

01:15:11.104 --> 01:15:15.827
tell you he got back up,

01:15:17.828 --> 01:15:19.689
that our intervention prevailed.

01:15:21.880 --> 01:15:25.301
And that he reestablished himself as the

01:15:25.341 --> 01:15:28.603
chosen one, as the anointed Messiah,

01:15:30.344 --> 01:15:33.706
as the son of God, our savior,

01:15:35.046 --> 01:15:36.106
then returning King.

01:15:36.546 --> 01:15:38.068
And I want you to celebrate him as

01:15:38.108 --> 01:15:38.448
such.

01:15:40.389 --> 01:15:41.128
Thank you for listening.